{
    "name": "Performer",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Performers captivate and entertain their audiences with a wide range of art forms, including singing, dancing, playing instruments, acrobatics, magic tricks, and more. While many celebrities rise to fame on digital platforms, performers thrive best in front of a live audience."
        },
        {
            "name": "Celebrities",
            "type": "section",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Interstellar Species",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Interstellar Species pg. 156",
                        "alt": "Interstellar Species pg. 156",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq02d4w?Starfinder-Interstellar-Species"
                    },
                    "page": 156
                }
            ],
            "html": "Celebrities shine in ways that often draw admiration, adoration, or amusement from fans across their home worlds and beyond. They regularly engage with fans through interviews, social media, and special appearances, boosting their sway in the court of public opinion. Some celebrities use their massive platforms to influence policy and elections, and it\u2019s not uncommon for groups with specific political or corporate interests to secretly plant or sponsor celebrities to advance particular agendas."
        }
    ],
