            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Three times per day as a full action, a performer can begin a captivating show that fascinates creatures within 60 feet (Will negates) for as long as the performer keeps performing (a standard action each round). Once during the effect\u2019s duration, the performer can continue performing as a full action instead of as a standard action to also impart a suggestion to one fascinated creature, as the spell (Will negates). This is a sense-dependent effect, and the suggestion effect is language-dependent.",
